----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
lua版本5.1

需要安装 luatz 库
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
使用终端的时候需要设置终端映射键，参考:
  1. https://www.reddit.com/r/neovim/comments/12hyi9t/make_scr_cscr_stab_ctab_work_in_neovim_kitty/
  2. https://www.reddit.com/r/neovim/comments/mbj8m5/how_to_setup_ctrlshiftkey_mappings_in_neovim_and/

以下配置以 windows terimal 为例:
{
  "actions": [
     {
      "command": {
        "action": "sendInput",
        "input": "\u001b[13;2u"
      },
      "keys": "shift+enter"
    },
    {
      "command": {
        "action": "sendInput",
        "input": "\u001b[13;5u"
      },
      "keys": "ctrl+enter"
    },
    {
      "command": {
        "action": "sendInput",
        "input": "\u001b[91;5u"
      },
      "keys": "ctrl+["
    },
    {
      "command": {
        "action": "sendInput",
        "input": "\u001b[88;5u"
      },
      "keys": "ctrl+shift+x"
    },
    {
      "command": {
        "action": "sendInput",
        "input": "\u001b[59;5u"
      },
      "keys": "ctrl+;"
    },
    {
      "command": {
        "action": "sendInput",
        "input": "\u001b[90;5u"
      },
      "keys": "ctrl+shift+z"
    },
    {
      "command": {
        "action": "sendInput",
        "input": "\u001b[80;5u"
      }
    },
    {
      "command": {
        "action": "sendInput",
        "input": "\u001b[58;5u"
      },
      "keys": "ctrl+shift+;"
    },
  ]
}
